dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Iron County, WI 2009
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Iron County, Wisconsin in 2009. it is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Iron_Hydro_2009'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Iron_HydroLine_2009', and 'Iron_HydroPoly_2009'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
